parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description:
The maximum number of entries per page.

Valid values: 1 to 100.

Default value: 20.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description:
The pagination token that is used in the next request to retrieve a new page of results.

If the total number of entries returned for the current request exceeds the value of the `MaxResults` parameter, the entries are truncated. In this case, you can use the `token` to initiate another request and obtain the remaining entries.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group.

parameters.name: SortCriterion
parameters.description: The method that is used to sort the entries returned.
